author: travelandtourworld.com
title: Aeromexico Reports September 2015 Traffic ResultsTravelandtourworld.com
text:
Aeromexico Reports September 2015 Traffic Results
Grupo Aeromexico S.A.B. de C.V. today reported September 2015 operational results.
Grupo Aeromexico transported 1 million 417 thousand passengers in September; a 6.0% year-on-year increase. International passenger numbers increased by 16.0%, while domestic passenger numbers increased by 1.8%.
Demand, measured in Revenue Passenger Kilometers (RPKs), increased by 9.8%, year-on-year. Aeromexico’s capacity, measured in Available Seat Kilometers (ASKs), increased by 10.9 % year-on-year.
Aeromexico’s September load factor was 77.4%.
